## What this is

A PWA (Progressive Web App) Sean built for his son Ryder to track his dyslexia homework. Ryder needs to do 20 minutes of homework on 5 of any 7 days, working toward a goal date of **31 March 2027**. The app lives on Ryder's iPad and laptop as a webapp and motivates him via streak tracking with real-world prizes.

