## Known limitations / future ideas

- **No "streak shield"** — one bad week kills the streak entirely. Could add a 1-per-month free pass.
- **No retroactive ticking** — he can only mark today done, not catch up on yesterday. Easy add if needed.
- **Single user** — designed for Ryder only. Multi-kid would need a user picker.
- **No notifications** — no daily reminder push. Could add via Web Push API but complex.
- **No parent oversight UI** — Sean can see the data via Cloudflare KV browser, but no nice parent view of "did Ryder tick honestly?". Could add a parent dashboard route.
- **Honour system** — no enforcement that he actually did 20 minutes. Trust-based.
- **No analytics / export** — could add a "download CSV" button for a year-end review.

